Menu_GetHelpMessage
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Menu=>menu/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Menu_GetHelpMessage
Veneer:	<menu_get_help_message>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = Menu object ID
r2 = 17
r3 = pointer to buffer
r4 = size of buffer
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r4 = size of buffer required (if r3=0)
     else buffer contains help message.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:		Method gets help text for the menu.